rows.label: qst700701_msg0201
rows.name:
Ah! Prince Adel!
Long have I longed for the chance to
speak with you properly!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0202
rows.name:
I'm really sorry, but we're actually
pretty busy, so...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0203
rows.name: No! Wait, please wait!!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0204
rows.name:
That's a bit rude, isn't it?! I mean, I'm
constantly going out of my mind with
worry about you, Prince, and now this?!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0205
rows.name:
It's, it's, it's heartless, is what it is!
And after I've pledged the entirety of
my heart and soul to you and Iira...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0206
rows.name:
...And another thing, I've been at your
side since your royal childhood, and
you've always been so, shall we say...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0207
rows.name: Cut to the chase already!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0208
rows.name:
Ahahah...
Right, yes, fine. Say what you
wanted to say, then.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0209
rows.name: Huh? Ah, right, indeed!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0210
rows.name:
The earlier attack has caused a lot of
damage to the capital, and the rubble is
still being removed...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0211
rows.name:
In particular, the residential and
shopping wards are taking time to
clear, but we're short-handed, so I...

rows.label: qst700701_msg0212
rows.name:
All right, I see the problem here.
How about we help out, then?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0213
rows.name: Egad! Would you really?!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0214
rows.name:
You said you need hands, right?
Well, the Prince and the rest of us have
some perfectly good ones right here.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0215
rows.name:
She's right.
I would like to do my part also.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0216
rows.name: I thank you, kind sir... Huh?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0217
rows.name: You! Aren't you the Superbian-?!

rows.label: qst700701_msg0218
rows.name:
Shhhhh... Let's not tell the whole
country about it, shall we?

rows.label: qst700701_msg0219
rows.name:
With this many helpers, we should be
done in no time.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0220
rows.name:
Quite. Let's clean up the wreckage
from the residential and shopping
wards, and let's be quick about it.

rows.label: qst700701_msg0221
rows.name: Oh my, oh my, oh myyy...
